@startuml memo-lifecycle
title Memo Lifecycle — Capture, Hygiene, Routing
skinparam defaultFontName Helvetica
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam BackgroundColor white
skinparam ArrowColor #111
skinparam ArrowFontColor #111
skinparam rectangle {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam database {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam usecase {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam card {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}
skinparam actor {
  BorderColor #111
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #111
}

actor "Human\nuser" as HumanUser
actor "Agent" as Agent #LightSkyBlue

rectangle "Mid-workflow\nobservation /\nidea / TODO" as Observation #FFFFFF;line.dashed

card "/livespec-impl-*:\ncapture-memo" as CaptureMemo #LightYellow
database "memo store\n(impl-plugin-specific:\nbd Dolt / JSONL / ...)" as MemoStore

card "/livespec:doctor" as Doctor #LightYellow
card "/livespec-impl-*:\nlist-memos\n[--keyword]\n[--untriaged --json]" as ListMemos #LightYellow

card "/livespec-impl-*:\nprocess-memos\n(per-memo dialogue)" as ProcessMemos #LightYellow
usecase "Per-memo\ndisposition?" as Disposition

card "/livespec:propose-changes\n(cross-namespace handoff)" as ProposeChanges #LightYellow
database "proposed_changes/\n(livespec-core)" as Proposed
database "work-item queue\n(joins implement\nqueue)" as WorkQueue
rectangle ".ai/<topic>.md\n+ AGENTS.md /\nCLAUDE.md reference" as AiTree #Lavender
rectangle "(deleted)" as Discarded #FFFFFF;line.dashed

HumanUser --> Observation
Observation --> CaptureMemo
Agent --> CaptureMemo : drives capture
CaptureMemo --> MemoStore

MemoStore -[#888,dashed]-> Doctor : --untriaged --json\nquery
Doctor --> HumanUser : warns about\nuntriaged memos\nbeyond N days
HumanUser --> ListMemos : (user-facing\nsearch)
ListMemos --> MemoStore : reads
MemoStore --> ListMemos

HumanUser --> ProcessMemos : invokes after\ndoctor warning
Agent --> ProcessMemos : per-memo handholding
ProcessMemos --> MemoStore : reads each untriaged
ProcessMemos --> Disposition

Disposition --> ProposeChanges : SPEC-BOUND\n(handoff to core)
ProposeChanges --> Proposed
Disposition --> WorkQueue : IMPL-BOUND\n(file work item;\npicked up by implement)
Disposition --> AiTree : PERSISTENT-KNOWLEDGE\n(write file + update\nAGENTS.md/CLAUDE.md ref)
Disposition --> Discarded : DISCARD\n(delete from store)

ProcessMemos --> MemoStore : marks each\nmemo processed

note right of MemoStore : Storage backend is impl-plugin-specific.\nbd Dolt for livespec-impl-beads.\nJSONL for livespec-impl-plaintext.\nGitLab note for livespec-impl-gitlab.\nUser-facing semantics are uniform across all.

note bottom of Doctor : Doctor's invariant:\n"no memo MUST remain\nuntriaged beyond N days."\nQueries the active impl plugin\nvia --untriaged --json. Doctor\nknows about memos ONLY to\ndetect-and-warn; resolution\nlives impl-side.

note right of AiTree : Persistent-knowledge file:\nnamed per topic, progressively\nloaded via AGENTS.md /\nCLAUDE.md reference. NOT a junk\ndrawer — each file has a focused\nsubject and explicit reach.

note bottom of Disposition : Four dispositions encode\nthe livespec philosophy:\neverything resolves to spec,\nimplementation, persistent\nknowledge, or oblivion.

@enduml
